{
  "text": "In this study, higher serum ferritin levels were associated with poor prognosis. Serum ferritin levels are correlated with the activity of CADM-associated ILD [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . White blood cell and neutrophil counts were not significantly different before and after PMX-DHP therapy. c, e: After PMX-DHP, the platelet counts in peripheral blood samples and serum HMGB-1 levels were significantly lower than before PMX-DHP therapy. d: Serum LDH levels were not significantly different before and after PMX-DHP. f: The P/F ratio tended to improve after PMX-DHP, but there were no significant differences between P/F ratio before and after PMX-DHP therapy. *: p value <0.05",
